法規內容.條文內容:
For an application for business tax exemption or entertainment tax reduction referred to in the previous Article to be approved, the following documents should be submitted:
1. application letter;
2. documents evidencing the conformation to the rules in the preceding Article; 
3. materials related to performing conducting cultural and artistic activities; 
4. the responsible person's identification papers; and
5. other documents as prescribed by the CCA. 
The application documents referred to in the preceding paragraph shall be submitted at least one month before the start of the activity, otherwise they will not be accepted.
